name: FRAGMENT #2: REGRET
description:
All done, but what else? What if unwanted things occur after everything has happened? What if my mind is going uncontrolled? What if I can't endure this feeling anymore? What if, and what if...
In the end, what have I done, my friend?

The second part of "Fragments of Fur". (2/4)
